In Q4 2023, 70,000 ALGO have been allocated from Folks Finance’s [Targeted DeFi Rewards](https://www.algorand.foundation/news/targeted-defi-rewards-implementation-report-1) to incentivize participation in Algorand consensus. The rewards will be distributed solely based on how many blocks users produce.

Participating in Algorand consensus means properly staking ALGO through a [node](https://www.algorand.foundation/news/what-is-a-node-in-blockchain). The ALGO will then be eligible to propose the creation of blocks or vote on the approval status of blocks.&#x20;

Read the details about eligibility in our [Medium article](https://medium.com/@folksfinance/how-to-join-algorand-consensus-to-earn-rewards-from-folks-finance-16d3fd957e00).

Here are the steps to join Consensus and start receiving rewards through Folks Finance

1. **Mint gALGO**

Users must be committed to Liquid Governance by minting gALGO. The opportunity to mint gALGO is only available during the first two weeks of each quarter, coinciding with the opening of a new Algorand governance period. If users do not currently have any minted gALGO, they will not be able to earn consensus rewards through Folks Finance until they get another chance to mint gALGO.

2. **Click on “◻ Consensus”**

In the corner of the "Your Commitment" box, users should see the word "Consensus" next to an icon of a cube. Users can click on this to open the modal where they will enter the necessary information to join consensus. It is important to ensure that the wallet used to mint gALGO is connected to the Folks app.

