# Airdrop

Claim your token here:

{% embed url="<https://claim.folks.finance/en>" %}

The Folks Finance airdrop is designed to reward the most active and engaged users while ensuring a fair and inclusive distribution for the entire community.

***

#### Distribution Methodology

Season 1 of the airdrop distributes 1,646,479 FOLKS tokens (3,29% of total supply), allocated across several eligibility criteria: Folks Points, Founders Pass NFT holders, and partner campaign winners (Okx Wallet, Haha Wallet, Zerion Wallet, Gate Wallet, Airaa mindshare campaign, Orbiter campaign, Galxe campaign).

Snapshot was taken on October 24th, 2025, at \~11:00 UTC. Points or NFTs obtained after this snapshot already count toward eligibility for future seasons.

Folks Points allocations are determined by users’ performance in the Leaderboard campaign, using a natural logarithm function to balance score disparities between top and mid-tier participants. Minimum eligibility is 1,000,000 points.

Each Founders Pass NFT grants 30 $FOLKS, cumulative by quantity. Addresses that also have ≥ 1 M points receive a bonus based on their NFT tier:

* 1 or more Silver NFTs → +10 $FOLKS
* 1 or more Gold NFTs → +20 $FOLKS
* 1 or more Black NFTs → +30 $FOLKS

If an NFT was held before the snapshot but is not linked to an xChain account or Algorand address, the allocation doesn’t show in the checker and won’t be possible to claim manually, but will be airdropped directly to that wallet shortly after claim goes live.

Partner campaign and NFT allocations are not subject to the Instant / Linear Unlock claim options — they are fully claimable immediately in both cases.

Rewards from Zerion Wallet and the Airaa mindshare campaign will be distributed directly by them. Follow their official channels for updates.

***

#### Claiming Options

Eligible users receive the airdrop full amount only if they decide to opt for a 3-month linear unlock. Alternatively, users have the option to instant claim and receive a partial amount.

The claim window (for both options) runs from November 6, 13:00 UTC to December 16, 14:00 UTC.\
For clarity, in the examples we will use a scenario where User A is eligible for a total airdrop allocation of 100 FOLKS.

**Instant Claim**\
Users receive 20% of their allocation immediately, with no further action required after claiming.

E.g. User A decides to Instant Claim and receives only 20 FOLKS from the total 100 FOLKS allocation.

**Linear Unlock Claim**

Users receive 10% of their allocation immediately, and the remaining 90% unlocks linearly over 90 days from the beginning of the unlock period.\
The unlock period runs from December 16th, 2025, at 14:00 UTC to March 16th, 2026, at 14:00 UTC, users can claim unlocked tokens at any time during this period.\
The claiming window will close on March 31st, 2026, at 14:00 UTC. Any unclaimed tokens after this date will be lost.

E.g. User A decides to opt for the Linear Unlock Claim. They receive 10 FOLKS immediately, then 1 FOLKS per day over the 90-day unlock period.

{% hint style="warning" %}
**General warnings:**

* Users must choose between Instant Claim and Linear Unlock Claim before December 16, 2025, at 13:00 UTC. Failure to make a choice by this deadline results in permanent loss of the entire airdrop allocation.
* Once a claim option is selected and confirmed, it cannot be changed.
* The Linear Unlock period begins on December 16, 2025, at 14:00 UTC, and continues for 90 days until March 16, 2026, at 14:00 UTC.
* Once the unlock period ends, users have until March 31, 2026, at 14:00 UTC to claim any remaining unlocked tokens. Any unclaimed tokens after this date will be permanently lost.
  {% endhint %}

